{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM03_ST2_060.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x2c,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Excuse me, what is this book all about...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Do you have rocks for brains? Are you seriously asking me a question that you can figure out by simply reading it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I-I'm sorry. Of course I'll read it myself later."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "It's just that...I wanted to know why you recommended this book to me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1cc,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "...Being interrupted while reading is my biggest pet peeve...but fine."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1cd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "This place has a lot of books that have been preserved in great condition. It's quite miraculous in this day and age."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1ce,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "This collection of books is immeasurable. It's like my own personal paradise."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I think I understand. But, what does any of that have to do with this book?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Well, while I had confined myself to this paradise, devouring its knowledge in peace..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1cf,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "A very noisy little girl came in one day."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Oh. That must've bothered you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Indeed, she did. So, I decided to give her a book to occupy her and send her on her way."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Was that little girl...? Did I really bother you that much?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1cf,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Precisely. In fact, even now, you continue to obstruct my studies."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Uhh, sorry... I didn't mean to disturb you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "However, I understand very well your thirst for knowledge."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I've perused all the books in this section, and so far, that is the most appropriate book for you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1d0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "That's why I recommended it to you. That's all there is to it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "(In this section... I wonder if he read all these books... Whoa...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "...Now I feel inclined to ask you a question, as well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Why did you come here?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "To synthesize... I want to learn proper alchemy. I've always taught myself, so..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Any alchemy book would've been fine, but I never thought there could be this many types of them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "But while I was talking to the librarian, my focus kinda shifted to a book on flowers..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "I think I might've gotten a little greedy. Hehehe..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Hmph, if you came here to find an answer, I'm afraid you'll find no such thing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Even with all these books? I came here hoping I'd find out something."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x91,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Naturally, you'll be able to find many fragments that will lead you to the answer."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x92,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "However, those fragments will only start to make sense once the seeker, herself, puts them all together."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x92,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Alchemy requires more than just passing attention. There are many principles that form its underlying foundation."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x93,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Furthermore, various methods exist between different practitioners, so the core heart of it is strictly hidden."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "In other words, I won't find \"this is the answer!\" in any of these books, will I?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Of course not. Don't forget that even in the past, few people had the ability to use alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "It certainly won't be as simple as perusing a book and finding the answer right in front of you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "I see... I guess it's not as easy as I thought it would be..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "Alchemy requires vast knowledge about the properties of objects and theories of how to transform those objects..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "As well as the inspiration to set foot toward the truth."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "Inspiration... So, just having the knowledge isn't enough...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "In any event, the basics begin with knowledge. And acquiring knowledge begins with observing the phenomena."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "That book will help you get started. Okay, that should be enough for now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "Leave before my mood sours."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "Oh, okay. Thank you very much..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "msg_string": "(Mr. Keith is scary...but I think this is the longest we've talked to each other.)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2b,
            "msg_string": "(I hope we can have a nicer conversation next time.)"
        }
    ]
}